Audible UK Privacy Notice
Last updated: 20 November 2024.
We know that you care how information about you is used and shared, and we appreciate your trust in us to do that carefully and sensibly. This Privacy Notice describes how we collect and process your personal information through Audible websites, products, services, and applications that reference this Privacy Notice (together “Audible Services”).
Controllers of Personal Information
What Personal Information About Customers Does Audible Europe Collect?
For What Purposes does Audible Europe Process Your Personal Information?
What About Cookies and Other Identifiers?
Does Audible Europe Share Your Personal Information?
How Secure is Information About Me?
What About Advertising?
What Information Can I Access?
What Choices Do I Have?
